OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FIt is all the more staggering because
OL,8,Fit is more than likely an
OL,9,Funderestimation.
OL,11,FCDOPs do not routinely ask about a
OL,12,Fchild's specific housing circumstances
OL,13,Fwhen assessing how they died. It is
OL,14,Fnot a mandatory question.
OL,16,FITV News Investigations Editor Dan
OL,17,FHewitt reports exclusively on the 55
OL,18,Fhomeless children who have died in
OL,19,Ftemporary accommodation since 2019
