OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FIt means in the 55 cases we know
OL,8,Fabout, the panel has gone out of their
OL,9,Fway to note in their written report
OL,10,Fthat the child was living in temporary
OL,11,Fhousing and that it was a factor in
OL,12,Ftheir death.
OL,14,FHow many other children have died in
OL,15,Fsimilar circumstances, but not been
OL,16,Frecorded in the same way?
OL,18,FThe All Party Parliamentary Group
OL,19,F(APPG) on Temporary Accommodation have
OL,20,Fnow successfully campaigned for that
OL,21,Fto change.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/14
