OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FFrom here on in, CDOPs will roundly
OL,8,Fask what's a child housing situation
OL,9,Fwas at the time of their death and
OL,10,Fwhether it may have been a factor.
OL,12,FDepressingly, it means the APPG
OL,13,Fpredicts that the 55 cases will rise.
OL,14,FEven without that change in approach
OL,15,Fby experts, the number has gone up.
OL,17,FIn January last year, the number of
OL,18,Fchildren who died as a result of being
OL,19,Fhomeless was 34.
