OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FIt has now increased by 21 after
OL,8,Fthousands more cases were reviewed by
OL,9,Fthe National Child Mortality Database
OL,10,Fwho analyses the reports of CODPs.
OL,12,F42 of the 55 were babies who had not
OL,13,Fyet reached their first birthday. No
OL,14,Fwords can convey the heartbreak of
OL,15,Fthose families. Each is a personal
OL,16,Ftragedy, and surely a preventable one?
OL,18,FWhat is being done about this?
