OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FA government spokesperson responded to
OL,8,Four report to say the findings were
OL,9,F"completely shocking".
OL,11,F"Our guidance to councils is clear
OL,12,Fthat all temporary accommodation must
OL,13,Fbe safe and suitable for families with
OL,14,Fbabies and have enough space for a
OL,15,Fcot," they added.
OL,17,FThat 42 babies who have died points to
OL,18,Fa serious issue with safe sleeping in
OL,19,Ftemporary accommodation (TA), say MPs
OL,20,Fand campaigners.
