OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FWhen children are moved into TA - a
OL,8,Fhostel, a bedsit, a private flat - it
OL,9,Fis usually a last minute move and they
OL,10,Fare given no choice but to accept by
OL,11,Ftheir local council. There is no
OL,12,Fguarantee the place they are sent to
OL,13,Fhas a cot or suitable bed for their
OL,14,Fbaby.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/14
