OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FIf a baby or infant sleeps in a cot or
OL,8,Fmoses basket, they are significantly
OL,9,Fless likely to die than if they slept
OL,10,Fin their parents' bed, in their
OL,11,Fparents' arms, or on a sofa, which is
OL,12,Fshown to increase the risk of Sudden
OL,13,FInfant Death Syndrome, or SIDS.
OL,15,FLast week, the government wrote to
OL,16,Flocal authorities changing the
OL,17,Fguidance to encourage them to only
OL,18,Fplace babies in accommodation with
OL,19,Fspace for a cot.
