OL,7,FThe APPG on Temporary Housing has
OL,8,Fwelcomed this change, but say the big
OL,9,Fissue is lack of enforcement. There is
OL,10,Fno regulator or organisation checking
OL,11,Fwhether cots are being made available
OL,12,Fto families.
