OL,7,FChair of the APPG and Labour MP
OL,8,FSiobhan McDonaugh said: "This
OL,9,Fintervention will only save lives if
OL,10,Fit is actually implemented. That is
OL,11,Fwhat we need to see now across local
OL,12,Fauthorities in England".
OL,14,FThe much wider issue here is a chronic
OL,15,Fshortage of affordable homes. There
OL,16,Fare more than 1 million households on
OL,17,Fthe waiting list for social homes.
