OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FThe number of children living in
OL,8,Ftemporary accommodation is at a record
OL,9,F142,000. Almost 20,000 of those are
OL,10,Fbabies under the age of one.
OL,12,FCash-strapped councils do not have
OL,13,Fenough housing for the number of
OL,14,Fpeople coming to them for help. They
OL,15,Fare having to fund places in TA out of
OL,16,Fever-dwindling budgets and it is
OL,17,Fleading to families being placed in
OL,18,Fever more unsuitable accommodation.
