OL,3,CGovernment says ITV News story on
OL,4,Cchild deaths in temporary homes is
OL,5,C'shocking'
OL,7,FIt explains why we found homeless
OL,8,Fchildren living in converted shipping
OL,9,Fcontainers in Ealing. The council says
OL,10,Fit was an innovative attempt at a
OL,11,Fsolution to the housing shortage.
OL,13,FIt is essentially a failed experiment
OL,14,F- the "modular homes" are now being
OL,15,Fdecommissioned as a direct result of
OL,16,Ffamilies rising concerns about the
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,19,FBritain needs more affordable housing.
OL,20,FEveryone agrees on that.
